 "Create the case story. A good case is one \nthat describes a controversy or sets the scene by describing the characters \ninvolved and the situation. It should also allow for some action to be taken \nin order to gain resolution of the situation.": "Vytvori\u0165 pr\u00edpadov\u00fa \u0161t\u00fadiu.\nDobr\u00fdm pr\u00edkladom je zachytenie kontroverznej situ\u00e1cie \nalebo sc\u00e9ny popisom chovania zainteresovan\u00fdch os\u00f4b. Mala by sa tie\u017e vzia\u0165 do \u00favahy \nmo\u017enos\u0165 reakcie, ktor\u00e1 napom\u00f4\u017ee vyrie\u0161eniu situ\u00e1cie.", 
